es are visible.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"There are two supported modes: autoScroll on\/off","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is true, the slices are automatically scrolled.  Subscribe to the delgate and listen for the scrolled callback, when you get it send another slice of text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"When autoScroll is false, you can drive the slices and how they look on the screen.  You can send all the slices at once or send one at a time and animate it onto the screen at the current time."}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"ScrollLayout","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"ScrollLayout"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://UltraliteSDK/documentation/UltraliteSDK/ScrollLayout/sendImage(image:slicePosition:scrollFirst:)":{"title":"sendImage(image:slicePosition:scrollFirst:)","url":"\/documentation\/ultralitesdk\/scrolllayout\/sendimage(image:sliceposition:scrollfirst:)","abstract":[{"text":"After sending scrollLayoutConfig, this will set the screen content according to those","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"configured parameters."}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/UltraliteSDK\/documentation\/UltraliteSDK\/ScrollLayout\/sendImage(image:slicePosition:scrollFirst:)","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sendImage","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"image","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGImageRef","text":"CGImage","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"text":"slicePosition","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"scrollFirst","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind